description: Enables the Amazon Inspector delegated administrator for your Organizations organization.

parameters.name: clientToken
parameters.description: The idempotency token for the request. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

parameters.name: delegatedAdminAccountId
parameters.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID of the Amazon Inspector delegated administrator.

nested_items.name: delegatedAdminAccountId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID of the successfully Amazon Inspector delegated administrator.
